{"tid":378119,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[討論]未來一兩年，香港附近會發生大地震?","createTime":"2017-08-28T08:42:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-06T07:02:29.000Z","uid":40010,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c949406b009587c17fb6f9f0c0886a5b9e94b45f","tid":378119,"uid":40010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T08:42:09.000Z","msg":"對上一次導致香港有損毀口嘅地震已經係1918年南澳大地震。<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/1918%E5%B9%B4%E5%8D%97%E6%BE%B3%E5%A4%A7%E5%9C%B0%E9%9C%87\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F1918%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E5%258D%2597%25E6%25BE%25B3%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%259C%25B0%25E9%259C%2587&d=VCEEgr%2Fo96oiOv6qgeZJdlzEg0sy7MJ6GkP0ogsbSqo%3D&h=f6e40067\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/1918%E5%B9%B4%E5%8D%97%E6%BE%B3%E5%A4%A7%E5%9C%B0%E9%9C%87</a><br />\n(又稱為汕頭大地震，係發生於1918年2月13日下午2時7分之南澳地震。其震央位於廣東省東部南澳島東北約10公里的海底，即北緯23.5度，東經117.2度，規模為7.5，震央震度為X。)<br />\n<br />\n(這次地震也是香港開埠後唯一一次造成明顯破壞的地震。當時時值春節，據記載地震發生時「正在慶賀新年的香港居民，見公共建築物、電話線搖動，多奔入街中。」香港不少建築物出現裂縫。這個地震也引發了地震海嘯。)<br />\n<br />\n雖然2010年都有發生后海灣地震。但係個次只有黎克特制2.8級。今年係2017年，同1918年嘅地震相差約100年。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果係地震帶之上發生黎克特制9.0或以上嘅周期係每10&ndash;50年1次。<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/%E9%87%8C%E6%B0%8F%E5%9C%B0%E9%9C%87%E8%A6%8F%E6%A8%A1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-hk%2F%25E9%2587%258C%25E6%25B0%258F%25E5%259C%25B0%25E9%259C%2587%25E8%25A6%258F%25E6%25A8%25A1&d=VCEEgr%2Fo96oiOv6qgeZJdlzEg0sy7MJ6GkP0ogsbSqo%3D&h=129818f8\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/%E9%87%8C%E6%B0%8F%E5%9C%B0%E9%9C%87%E8%A6%8F%E6%A8%A1</a><br />\n不過，香港唔屬於地震帶，但係同上次1918年黎克特制6.0以上嘅地震相差100年，相信地底應該累積一定壓力。所以，我覺得香港未來一兩年附近可能會發生黎克特制6.0以上嘅地震。而震度可能係麥加利地震震度6級或以上。<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/%E9%BA%A5%E5%8A%A0%E5%88%A9%E5%9C%B0%E9%9C%87%E7%83%88%E5%BA%A6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-hk%2F%25E9%25BA%25A5%25E5%258A%25A0%25E5%2588%25A9%25E5%259C%25B0%25E9%259C%2587%25E7%2583%2588%25E5%25BA%25A6&d=VCEEgr%2Fo96oiOv6qgeZJdlzEg0sy7MJ6GkP0ogsbSqo%3D&h=0ef42b51\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/%E9%BA%A5%E5%8A%A0%E5%88%A9%E5%9C%B0%E9%9C%87%E7%83%88%E5%BA%A6</a><br />\n<br />\n由於地震冇預警，香港人又覺得香港一定冇大型地震。所以對於地震呢個天災防範會好低。加上，香港係沿海地方，好易會有海潚。<br />\n<br />\n利申：自己整合資料有感而發<br />\n<br />\n歡迎討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d840542538d6f19d141710d9d51df8a171648ed8","tid":378119,"uid":36441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T10:45:54.000Z","msg":"河源起完水壩都係咁地震 會唔會有助釋放壓力"},{"pid":"76d8c9faee62942af16f095cf8ef3bb050f4b33d","tid":378119,"uid":91432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T10:47:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52b08cd1b153103d0f13b59b9a663661ddb740bd","tid":378119,"uid":31429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T10:52:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"299d4e002b2469de289cf1ee45f4fd699b7c0b2d","tid":378119,"uid":1643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T12:35:46.000Z","msg":"2019 年 5 月 23 日<br />\n早上 9:00<br />\n中環 7 級地震<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/supplement/health/art/20101130/14713933\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fsupplement%2Fhealth%2Fart%2F20101130%2F14713933&d=VCEEgr%2Fo96oiOv6qgeZJdlzEg0sy7MJ6GkP0ogsbSqo%3D&h=8e594790\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fsupplement%2Fhealth%2Fart%2F20101130%2F14713933&h=523da3a1\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/supplement/health/art/20101130/14713933</a>"},{"pid":"fe88fc236a1553b750496146e2845abfb537d3a9","tid":378119,"uid":33714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T09:08:16.000Z","msg":"仲有唔夠一年時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a98a6b6849ca56c007cf0f3e3e622b68185bafd9","tid":378119,"uid":46801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T01:36:16.000Z","msg":"好驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60402e55a4cbe39eb5d56cce96eb222714e0576f","tid":378119,"uid":40010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T07:02:29.000Z","msg":"兩年前開左呢個post,感覺到係今年"}]}